Method Detail

getLabel

static String getLabel(String sec,
                       Character sub)
Returns label for section sec and (optionaly) subsection sub.

Parameters:
sec - Section code, MUST NOT be null.
sub - Subsection code, MAY be null.
Returns:
If sub is null, the label corresponding to section sec. Otherwise, the label of subsection sub in section sec.

isValidCategory

static boolean isValidCategory(String sec,
                               Character sub)
Checks if the given section and (optionaly) subsection codes are valid.

Parameters:
sec - Section code
sub - Subsection code
Returns:
If sub is null: true if section sec is valid. If sub is not null: true is the corresponding section and subsection are valid. Otherwise, false.
